As much as these 2 love playing outside, we are disinfecting our property and this calls for an indoor playdate. Bonnie is here for a visit, she is the granddaughter of Madrid

We welcomed Valentino into our family some time ago, but only now is he ready to start his OFA testing and join our program. I am excited for this journey with this fire-red boy #cavalierkingcharlesspaniel #cavaliers #dogsofinstagram #puppiesofinstagram #cavaliersofinstagram

We are expecting babies any minute ❤️ giving the mom a relaxing bath, setting up the area in which she will deliver her angels and letting her nest are the steps to start this beautiful journey that will last for about 10-12 weeks. She will sleep in our room where we can help her once the times comes and where we can safely watch the newborn babies. Once she delivers the little ones the setup changes and momma and puppies move to a whelping box where she can stay with the puppies or leave for a couple minutes to get a break. It’s a remarkable time that we treat with awe so join us for our journey and let’s raise this litter together❤️. Comment below on what you’d like to see with this litter and it will help us show our beautiful cavalier community what it’s like to raise these angels #cavalierkingcharlesspaniel #cavaliercommunity #cavalierworld #cavalierpuppy #cavalierpuppiesofinstagram #dogsofinstagram #puppiesofinstagram #puppy

We’ve had many requests to show how the delivery process goes. It can be a fairly quick process (our record was 2 hours of active labor with 🐶🐶🐶🐶🐶🐶 puppies) or it can be a long one (longest was around 23 hours from first puppy to last puppy). In our home, mommas almost always go into labor at night. The environment is calm ❤️. The kids and other dogs are asleep and they can have their peaceful delivery. We are always present for delivery and can lend a helping hand when needed (like breaking the sack, cutting off the umbilical cord, wiping the puppy down, showing them how to latch). In the morning, everyone wants to meet the new arrivals and welcome them into our family. #cavalierpuppy #cavaliers #puppy #cavalierkingcharlesspaniel #newbornpuppies #breeder #dog #responsiblebreeders #cavaliersofinstagram #dogsofinstagram #puppiesofinstagram

I’ve been scrolling through my videos while making sure the chubster in our newborn litter isn’t taking away “Tiny’s” seat at the milk bar and remembered about this video. This is a great example of the suffering we have to go through to get families photos of their puppy. We get brutally attacked… mauled, I would say. We drown in serotonin and there isn’t a rescue from this sort of drowning… And I’d do it over and over and over again #cavalierkingcharlesspaniel #cavalierpuppy #dogsofinstagram #puppiesofinstagram #cavalierofinstagram #cavalier #puppyphotography

One thing I have loved to witness over the last 4 years is how happy children are when they live side-by-side to dogs. The compassion they have is something every adult should learn from. In our home there will never be a hungry puppy, a sad puppy, an uncomfortable puppy, a puppy that is left without attention and the children are constantly making sure of that throughout the day❤️ #cavaliers #puppiesofinstagram #cavaliersofinstagram #dogsofinstagram #cavalierpuppy #cavalierpuppies #cavalierkingcharlesspaniel
